				<div class="elementor-widget-container">
									By covering these key areas, the ACSCP® exam ensures that candidates are not only proficient in traditional supply chain functions but also prepared to integrate cutting-edge AI technologies to drive efficiency, innovation, and competitiveness.								</div>
