					<div class="elementor-column elementor-col-50 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-02091a7" data-id="02091a7" data-element_type="column" data-e-type="column">
			<div class="elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated">
						<div class="elementor-element elementor-element-d78fe89 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading" data-id="d78fe89" data-element_type="widget" data-e-type="widget" data-widget_type="heading.default">
				<div class="elementor-widget-container">
					<h3 class="elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default">Why Would You Benefit from ACSCP®?</h3>				</div>
				</div>
				<div class="elementor-element elementor-element-3b6021d elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor" data-id="3b6021d" data-element_type="widget" data-e-type="widget" data-widget_type="text-editor.default">
				<div class="elementor-widget-container">
									The American Certified Supply Chain Professional (ACSCP®) certification positions you for success in one of the fastest-growing industries. According to the U.S. Bureau of Labor Statistics, supply chain jobs are projected to grow 11% between 2019 and 2029, adding over 531,200 new positions. By earning the ACSCP®, you gain the expertise to help your organization build a resilient and sustainable supply chain, ready to navigate disruptions and seize new opportunities. This certification not only enhances your career prospects but also equips you to drive innovation and operational excellence in a rapidly evolving business environment.
								</div>
				</div>
					</div>
		</div>
